import { ReactElement } from 'react'; export function News(): ReactElement { return ( <>

News

Nov. 2022: Prof. Shing-Chi Cheung elected as an{' '} IEEE Fellow

Prof. Shing-Chi Cheung has been elected as an IEEE Fellow in November 2022.

  • Jan. 2024: Jiajun Hu and Jialun Cao have successfully defended their PhD thesis.
  • Nov. 2023: One paper is accepted by IEEE S&P 2024.
  • Jul. 2023: Three papers are accepted by ESEC/FSE 2023. Congrats to Ying, Ming, Jialun and Xiao.
  • Jul. 2023: Huaxun Huang has successfully defended his PhD thesis.
  • Jul. 2023: Two papers are accepted by ACM TOSEM. Congrats to Victor and Hengcheng.
  • Jul. 2023: One paper on software testing using LLM is accepted by ASE'23. Congrats to Tsz-On.
  • Jul. 2023: Yongqiang Tian has successfully defended his PhD thesis.
  • Jul. 2023: Prof. Shing-Chi Cheung has been promoted to chair professorship.
  • Jun. 2023: One paper is accepted by TOSEM.
  • May. 2023: Three papers are accepted by ISSTA'23.
  • May. 2023: Multiple papers are accepted by ACM TOSEM and IEEE TSE.
  • Nov. 2022: Prof. Shing-Chi Cheung has been elected to the IEEE Fellow Class 2023.
  • Oct. 2022: One paper accepted to ASE 2022.
  • Aug. 2022: Lili Wei became Assistant Professor at McGill University.
  • Aug. 2022: One paper is accepted by USENIX Security 2022.
  • May. 2022: Three papers are accepted by ICSE 2022.
  • Jul. 2021: Two papers are accepted by ASE'21.
  • May. 2021: Two papers are accepted by FSE'21.
  • May. 2021: One paper is accepted by Empirical Software Engineering.
  • May. 2021: One paper got ICSE'21 Distinguished paper award.
  • Sep. 2020: Yongqiang Tian published a{' '} repo{' '} for awesome machine learning materials
  • Oct. 2019: Lili Wei received{' '} SENG interview
  • May. 2019: Yongqiang Tian received Microsoft Cloud Software Research Fellow Award
  • Mar. 2019: Ming Wen passed his PhD thesis defense. Congratulations!
  • Oct. 2018: Lili Wei received 2018 Microsoft PhD Fellowship Award
  • Oct. 2018: Lili Wei received{' '} 2018 Google PhD Fellowship Award
  • Jul. 2018: {' '} CIDER accepted to ASE 2018
  • Jul. 2018: {' '} ωDroid{' '} accepted to ASE 2018
  • Dec. 2018: {' '} CapGen accepted to ICSE 2018
  • Nov. 2017: {' '} ChangeLocator {' '} accepted to EMSE
  • Jun. 2017: {' '} OASIS accepted to FSE 2017
  • Nov. 2016: A large collection of resource leaks bugs in real-world Android apps,{' '} DroidLeaks, has been released
  • Jul. 2016: Locus and{' '} FicFinder {' '} accepted to ASE 2016
  • Jun. 2016: Elite accepted to FSE 2016 and evaluated as a Platinum Artifact by the Artifact Evaluation Committee
  • Apr. 2016: CSNIPPEX {' '} accepted to ISSTA 2016 and artifact evaluated by the Artifact Evaluation Committee
  • Jan. 2016: CUSTODES and AutoConTest accepted to ICSE 2016
  • Oct. 2015: Casper accepted to POPL 2016
  • Oct. 2014: Yanyan Jiang received 2014 Microsoft Research Asia Fellowship Award
); }
